I think it might be a good idea to verify the actual differences for the plan. I tried using `git diff -- docs/plan...`, but there was no output. The line list seems sufficient, though. I could run `git diff -- src/loopService.js --stat` or even `git diff --numstat src/loopService.js`, which could help—although it isn't strictly necessary. I should inspect the plan further to be sure.
